game.name: Princess Indian Gala Fashion
game.description:
Ariel, Elana and Moana have returned here after a long time on the request of our beloved users. These three beautiful princesses have got the invitation from the popular Bollywood gala event. They have lots of preparations to take care of for since these beauties have visited Indian today. So, they have hired you as their personal assistant. Do you think that you are the right choice to handle this task? Join Princess Indian Gala Fashion and be prepared to get them ready for the gala event with bollywood stars tonight!
Remember these gorgeous princesses do not have enough knowledge how to put on the Indian traditional clothing. Browse through their wider and fine collection of outfits and accessories to help them wear perfect Indian looks in this HTML5 dressing game! Start with Moana and dress her up with an elegant dark-turquoise suit and salwar with a nice flower print on the bottom and combine her look with a pair of light blue flats and a statement gold necklace and a pair of matching earrings!
Now give Elana an excellent hairstyle and choose a yellow suit with detailed embroidery on the top and bottom and a blue pajami. Complete her look with a pair of cream sandals, and delicate golden jewelry! Hurry up ladies, Ariel is also waiting for her turn! Give her a light blue suit with a jacket with elegant embroidery work! Choose a nice matching hairstyle and pair it with a small necklace, statement earrings and a pair of suitable sandals in this cool princess dress-up game! Good luck to create the jaw-dropping Indian traditional looks for the princesses and have fun without download!
